Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.26,0:02:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...head for the New World,\Nthe second half of the Grand Line.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.94,0:03:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, no one has ever fully explored it\Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.32,0:03:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned\Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.40,0:03:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and his friends venture into that sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.77,0:03:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take down one of the Four Emperors -\Nthe rulers of the New World,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.88,0:03:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others formed a pirate alliance\Nwith Trafalgar Law.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.35,0:03:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Planning to hand over Caesar,\Nwho they caught in Punk Hazard,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.41,0:03:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and to destroy the factory\Nproducing the deadly weapon - SMILE,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.02,0:03:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}they came to Dressrosa -\Nthe kingdom that Doflamingo rules.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.02,0:03:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.09,0:03:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Flare-Flare Fruit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.10,0:04:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"A Dangerous Love!\NThe Dancer Girl - Violet!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.09,0:04:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The champion will get a Devil Fruit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, it's none other than "Fire-Fist" Ace's\NFlare-Flare Fruit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, here in this Colosseum,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.74,0:04:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we have tough fighters from the New World\Nwho were summoned by our king
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.15,0:04:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and brave participants from the public\Nwho are confident of their ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.92,0:04:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They will be divided into separate blocks
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.21,0:04:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the winners of each block \Nwill get to go to the next round.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, they can't have this valuable prize\Nso easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's theirs for the taking - if they can!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.77,0:05:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The gladiators that they're gonna fight\Nare not the ordinary bunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.64,0:05:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones who are gonna fight\Nthe winners of each block are...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the Don Quixote Family...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.82,0:05:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Señor Pink!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dellinger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lao G.!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Machvise!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.68,0:05:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the hero of the Colosseum...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.96,0:06:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Diamante!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.17,0:06:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Diamante-{\i0}sama{\i1}!\N--Diamante!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.97,0:06:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just start already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We wanna see a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.01,0:06:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't wait any longer!\NJust start a match already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.93,0:06:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did Ace's Flare-Flare Fruit get here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.57,0:06:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard there are no two
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.31,0:06:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Devil Fruits of the same \Npower existing at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.81,0:06:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.11,0:06:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when a Devil Fruit eater dies,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a Devil Fruit with the power that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the deceased possessed will pop \Nup again somewhere in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.45,0:07:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when somebody eats it,\Nhe'll become the new holder of that power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After "Fire-Fist" Ace died,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Flare-Flare Fruit was,\Nwithout anyone knowing, reproduced
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Young Master-{\i1}sama{\i0} got hold of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.93,0:07:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe the Young Master-{\i1}sama{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,made the Logia type Devil Fruit \Na prize for the competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can possess such incredible power,\Nmy life will change!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna let you eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I remember. Ace was your...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.46,0:07:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want it! The Flare-Flare Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.84,0:08:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! Why don't you eat it, Franky?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.34,0:08:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna lose my ability to swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.01,0:08:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ate the Gum-Gum Fruit so \NI can't eat another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.72,0:08:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't want some stranger \Nto possess Ace's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a memento of him to you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible that it's a trap\Nconsidering the way
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo dangled it in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.81,0:08:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have something that you'll \Nwant very badly now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.68,0:08:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But one thing is for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't let the chance slip by!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.72,0:08:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't wanna regret it afterward.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to go to the Colosseum anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.93,0:08:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just go there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.83,0:08:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.67,0:09:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.40,0:09:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think you can have it just because
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.38,0:09:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you want it, no one would \Nbe risking their life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.87,0:09:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate the \Nlevel of the competitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:14.08,Copy of Ep Title,,0000,0000,0000,,THE GROUP THAT WENT AFTER \NTHE MYSTERIOUS FAIRY
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They call it a fairy?! \NIt's just a dirty thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.61,0:09:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.31,0:09:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.05,0:09:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said "Wait"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.05,0:09:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give up a sword or two!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.49,0:09:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.29,0:09:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let it get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.39,0:10:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop striking off on your own!\NWe don't have that much time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.57,0:10:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.70,0:10:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find the fairy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.94,0:10:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she must be a goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.28,0:10:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:36.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,A DANCER - VIOLET
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.99,0:11:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How fascinating!\N--How intense!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.87,0:11:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the best dancer in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.05,0:12:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.59,0:12:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.23,0:12:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.89,0:12:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard that women in this country stab men,\Ndidn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.30,0:12:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A guy like you will get stabbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.07,0:12:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind getting stabbed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.41,0:12:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! I lost him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.12,0:12:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That stray Moss Head!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.45,0:12:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a good chance.\NLet's leave him on this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.33,0:12:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried as best as I could to catch him.\NI made a sincere effort!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.48,0:13:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many couples around here!\NI'm jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish Nami-{\i1}san{\i0} and Robin-{\i1}chan{\i0} suddenly\Nbecame attracted to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.16,0:13:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.43,0:13:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We caught each other's eye earlier,\Ndidn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.67,0:13:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Hold me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.10,0:13:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.33,0:13:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did she go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:14:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She must've slipped out the back door\Nto this Lover's Alley!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.94,0:14:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think she went that far yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.01,0:14:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We can't let her leave the town!\N--Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.55,0:14:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! They're gone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me. You can let go of me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.32,0:14:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... It's {\i1}really{\i0} my pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.53,0:14:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! Did you hit \Nyour head or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.33,0:14:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's just meeting you \Ncomes as a shock to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.74,0:14:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're bleeding a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.84,0:14:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.88,0:14:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.35,0:14:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I can't help falling in love!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! No, you shouldn't \Nlook at me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.86,0:14:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have already given up on love!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:14:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the men who have gotten \Ninvolved with me are…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.46,0:15:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.40,0:15:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were all happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.23,0:15:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were looking for you! Who were they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.27,0:15:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me if there's something \NI can do to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was this man and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.32,0:15:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...stabbed him after things went sour.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.59,0:15:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.52,0:15:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's true that women in this
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.14,0:15:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,country are so passionate about \Nlove that they'd stab a man for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.49,0:15:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Okay!\N--Okay?! Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.23,0:15:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't be so nice to a bad woman like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.57,0:15:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.37,0:15:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or I will... fall for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.31,0:15:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BANG!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.62,0:16:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you escort me to the next town\Nif you don't mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.23,0:16:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next town?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.93,0:16:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I want you to kill someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.94,0:16:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.98,0:16:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't care if it's a \Nnational treasure or not!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.79,0:16:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't allow myself to lose the Shusui!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.99,0:16:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Boy! First, we saw toys living side-by-side\Nwith humans{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.13,0:16:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and now, a thieving fairy?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.70,0:16:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn! What an annoying island!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.17,0:16:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was fairies who took your stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.03,0:16:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.87,0:16:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to turn a blind \Neye to whatever they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.84,0:16:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If it was a fairy or not,\NI'm gonna catch it and...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:16:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, I'm gonna chop it up\Nto get the sword back!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.32,0:17:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! You thief-fairy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.16,0:17:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Dear Nami-san and Robin-chan."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"I hope you will forgive this sinful man."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.50,0:17:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"I finally... finally...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.91,0:17:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...met the love of my life!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.35,0:17:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.69,0:17:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I was born to protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.93,0:17:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I love this romantic island - Dressrosa!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:18:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will get the national treasure of the Wano Kingdom\Nback for sure!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.04,0:18:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But first, I have to rescue Kanjuro\Nwho is held captive by Doflamingo's clan!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.55,0:18:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanjuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.38,0:18:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you rushing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.62,0:18:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was trying to show her \Naffection for me apparently!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.76,0:18:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How aggressive! But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come stop by for a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.37,0:18:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I shouldn't allow myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.20,0:18:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yielding to a young lady's temptation is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a dishonor to a warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?! Kanjuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.12,0:18:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.65,0:18:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister, you can't just come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.99,0:18:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're closed now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.76,0:18:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have some stuff to cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.26,0:18:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the knives and frying \Npans are not well maintained.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.33,0:18:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They haven't even washed their dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.90,0:19:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the guys. No wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.34,0:19:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna cook for\Nthe most wonderful lady in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.44,0:19:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of this kitchen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.78,0:19:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with us cooks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.79,0:19:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.62,0:19:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You{\i0} shouldn't mess with a cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.43,0:19:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me use this kitchen for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to keep you waiting, Violet-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.64,0:19:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think dancing requires stamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.58,0:19:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy this tasty and nutritious special dish!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.48,0:19:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.19,0:19:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You thief-fairy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.02,0:19:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moss Head?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.39,0:19:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.70,0:20:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanjuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.23,0:20:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kin'emon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.03,0:20:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.77,0:20:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no. Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.81,0:20:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wasn't planning to go off on my own.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.45,0:20:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Forgive me, Luffy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because it's destiny!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.72,0:20:24.85,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE CORRIDA COLOSSEUM
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.15,0:20:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.65,0:20:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a huge Colosseum!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.06,0:20:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of competition is it gonna be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.66,0:20:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people are going nuts!\NThat makes me wanna enter the competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.66,0:20:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're going crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.73,0:20:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's making it harder for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.24,0:20:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.24,0:20:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You infamous wanted toy soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.74,0:20:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't shoot me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.98,0:20:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jet Walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.40,0:21:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are too slow! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.84,0:21:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have my foot in the Colosseum!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.20,0:21:19.68,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE ONE-LEGGED SOLDIER\NAKA THE ANGRY LIGHTNING SOLDIER
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.44,0:21:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know the law, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.41,0:21:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police and the Navy are not allowed\Nin the Colosseum!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.48,0:21:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if a criminal is in the Colosseum,\Nit's not your jurisdiction!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.62,0:21:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only rule of law in here\Nis that of the Don Quixote Family!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.66,0:21:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you pull that trigger,\Nyou will become a criminal yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.13,0:21:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.13,0:21:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This island is so strange.\NThey put a toy on the wanted list?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.04,0:21:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he's very arrogant for a toy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.61,0:22:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, elderly people!\NDo you want me to carry your bag or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.65,0:22:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? He became polite all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.69,0:22:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a funny toy soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.59,0:22:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.79,0:22:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.36,0:22:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about this? Or this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.43,0:22:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey buddy, get out of our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.70,0:22:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I was in your way. I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.21,0:22:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're blushing so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.74,0:22:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a serious guy, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.38,0:22:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.78,0:22:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toys have to make people smile!\NThere is no such a thing as a serious toy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.26,0:22:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He took it personally!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.09,0:22:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're closing entries from the public\Nfor today's competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.97,0:22:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think anyone from the public wants to enter.\NThey're all cowards!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.64,0:22:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Luffy!\NI guess we have to go in separately.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.11,0:23:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.11,0:23:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here, here! I want to enter!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.81,0:23:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Enter! Enter! Enter! Enter!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.78,0:23:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.05,0:23:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.02,0:23:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you don't! You're too old!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.02,0:23:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
